adaptation-droidian-pipa (0.9-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Remove module-device-manifest from PulseAudio config (module doesn't
    exist in Droidian's PulseAudio 14.2 build).
  * Keep module-dbus-protocol (not loaded by default.pa, needed for
    GVC to communicate with PulseAudio).
  * GNOME Settings sound panel issue is a Droidian packaging bug in
    gnome-control-center (template references non-existent headphone_group
    widget), not an audio config issue.

 -- Ayman RGAB <aymanrgab@gmail.com>  Tue, 23 Jun 2026 21:00:00 +0000

